{"word":"ἀργία","slug":"ἀργία","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀργία</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>= <a href='S:ἀεργία'><el>ἀεργία</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>idleness, laziness</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b>in good sense, <i>rest, leisure</i>, <el>ἔργων</el> from work, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}